<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火德星君从天上飞了下来，他抓住了蝾螈，捡起了瓶子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这只蝾螈是从玉皇大帝的莲花池里逃出来的。” 火德星君向他们说明，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个瓶子是太上老君的，被这只蝾螈偷走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要把他们一起带回去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，火德星君就飞回了天上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！” 罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多村民跑了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们除掉了妖怪！” 一个女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们住在附近的一个村子里。请参加我们的宴会吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒流下了口水：“好吃的面条、蔬菜，还有饺子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“终于可以野餐了。” 玛拉开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看我。” 八戒端起一碗面条，一下子全倒进嘴里。呼噜！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒！” 悟净说，“注意点儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 八戒打了一个大大的嗝，玛拉哼哼笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也经常制造麻烦。” 杰克对悟空说，“我在学校永远坐不住。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了：“我也曾经因为坐不住被批评了很多次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你试试冥想吧，它会帮你安静下来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空告诉杰克要如何闭上眼睛慢慢呼吸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，杰克感到自己飘在空中。他睁大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇哦！” 杰克说，“我在飞——像火箭女孩儿一样！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是法术！” 悟空笑着让杰克落了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西。” 特勒尔小声说，“你消失的时候就是来到这个世界了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西点了点头：“我被困在这里和那个妖怪战斗了一段时间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要是我能帮你就好了。” 特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你帮不了我，特勒尔。那个妖怪非常强大。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“打扰一下，火箭女孩儿。” 悟净走过来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在你离开之前，能教教我如何从眼睛里发出火吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我试试。” 罗西说着，离开桌子，跟悟净去了别的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔深深地叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧在他的旁边坐下：“怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想帮助火箭女孩儿，但是我没有超能力。” 特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也没有超能力。” 唐僧说，“但是这不代表我不能帮助我的徒弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空、八戒和悟净很久以前犯下了可怕的罪行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在我正在帮助他们向善，让他们得到原谅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我相信你也一定会找到帮助朋友的方法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也希望。” 特勒尔点了点头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但其实他依然没有信心，他已经试过很多次去帮助罗西了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，唐僧师徒们要继续去西天取经了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空打开了传送门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见！” 大家同时说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西对悟空笑了笑：“要努力向善哦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，伙伴们！” 罗西在美罗城公园找到了她的朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克扬了扬眉：“你怎么知道我们在这里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了咽口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！” 她心想，“要怎么说？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我告诉罗西的。” 特勒尔马上说，“嗯，我刚才给罗西打电话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她去了叔叔家，刚回来，所以我就让她来这里找我们了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西点了点头：“对，就是这样！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西感激地看向特勒尔：“谢谢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔的脸上露出开心的笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西。” 玛拉说，“我们有一个神奇的故事要告诉你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克兴奋地点了点头：“你会后悔自己错过了什么！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>